## Typography

**Two fonts only.** Add via Google Fonts or `@fontsource`:

```
Display/Numbers: "DM Serif Display" — hero amounts, large metrics
Body/UI:         "DM Sans" — labels, tabs, paragraphs, buttons
Mono (keep):     "JetBrains Mono" — only for raw data tables, code-like values
```

**Type Scale (Tailwind classes):**

|Role        |Class                                                    |Usage                          |
|------------|---------------------------------------------------------|-------------------------------|
|Hero Number |`text-5xl font-bold` (DM Serif)                          |Take home, main metric         |
|Section Hero|`text-3xl font-semibold` (DM Serif)                      |Card primary value             |
|Card Label  |`text-xs font-medium tracking-widest uppercase` (DM Sans)|“TAKE HOME”, “WEEKLY LEFT”     |
|Body        |`text-sm` (DM Sans)                                      |Descriptions, subtitles        |
|Sublabel    |`text-xs text-text-secondary` (DM Sans)                  |“per week · all events applied”|
|Tab         |`text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase` (DM Sans)|OVERVIEW, MONTHLY, etc.        |
|Data Table  |`text-sm font-mono` (JetBrains Mono)                     |Monthly breakdown table        |

**Rule:** Monospace is banned outside of data tables. No exceptions.

