## Spacing & Layout

Chime’s secret is **generous padding and one big thing per card**.

```
Base unit: 4px (Tailwind default)

Card padding:       p-5 (20px) minimum, p-6 on larger cards
Card gap:           gap-3 between cards, gap-4 between sections
Section gap:        mt-8 between major sections
Border radius:      rounded-2xl (16px) for cards, rounded-xl (12px) for buttons/chips
```

**Card density rule:** Each card should communicate ONE primary number and ONE supporting label. If you have more than that, it’s two cards.

