## Component Patterns

### Metric Card

```
bg-bg-surface  rounded-2xl  p-5  border border-border-subtle
├── LABEL (text-xs, tracking-widest, text-secondary, uppercase)
├── $VALUE (text-4xl, DM Serif, gold or green)
└── sublabel (text-xs, text-secondary)
```

### Section Header

```
gold left border (border-l-2 border-gold pl-3)
+ text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-secondary
```

### Tab Bar (OVERVIEW / MONTHLY / WEEKLY)

```
Inactive: text-text-disabled, no background
Active:   text-gold, border-b-2 border-gold
Hover:    text-text-primary transition-colors
Animation: border slides under on tab change (use Framer Motion layoutId)
```

### Navigation Bar (bottom)

```
bg-bg-surface  border-t border-border-subtle
Active icon: gold fill
Inactive icon: text-secondary
Label: text-[10px] tracking-wide uppercase
```

### Modal Shell (overlay dialogs)

```
Backdrop: rgba(0,0,0,0.72)+, full-viewport fixed overlay
Container: bg-bg-surface, border border-border-subtle, rounded-2xl, p-5
Header: text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-secondary
Primary action: green/gold solid fill with dark text
Secondary action: bg-bg-raised + subtle border
```

### Auth Shell (login/recovery)

```
Full-screen centered card on bg-bg-base
Card: max-width ~360px, bg-bg-surface, rounded-xl+, border-border-subtle
Brand eyebrow: gold uppercase tracking
Field labels: lS pattern, inputs: iS pattern
OAuth + credential actions use shared uppercase button rhythm
```

### Wizard Step Shell (setup/life-events)

```
Single-column step card flow, generous vertical gap (12–20px)
Pill/toggle controls use raised backgrounds + accent borders on active
Two-column field rows collapse to one column on smaller screens (future-proof)
Step actions pinned consistently at bottom of viewport/card
```

### Profile Detail Surfaces

```
BackBar: compact top row with gold back affordance + uppercase section title
DetailCard: grouped rows with subtle separators and rounded surface container
DetailRow: label left (text-secondary), value right (text-primary/status color)
Danger action (sign out): red border/accent, high-contrast icon + label
```

