## What NOT to Do (Common Mistakes)

- ❌ Full-width monospace text blocks outside tables
- ❌ More than 2 font families
- ❌ Cards with 4+ data points
- ❌ Uppercase on body text or paragraphs
- ❌ Border radius below `rounded-xl` on cards
- ❌ Animations that exceed 500ms (except number countup)
- ❌ Gold background fills (gold is text/border only, never bg)
- ❌ Mixing `text-white` and `text-text-primary` — pick one system

-----

## Implementation Priority

1. **Font swap** — biggest immediate visual impact, 30 min
1. **Color config** — update tailwind.config.js once, fixes everywhere
1. **Card component refactor** — build one `<MetricCard>` component, replace all
1. **Spacing pass** — increase padding across all cards
1. **Framer Motion install + number countup** — highest wow factor
1. **Tab animation** — polish, do last

