## Claude Code Prompt Strategy

Break into separate sessions per priority item above. Example starter:

> “Refactor all metric cards in `IncomePanel.tsx` to use the new MetricCard component pattern from the design spec. Card padding p-5, rounded-2xl, bg-bg-surface, one primary number in DM Serif text-4xl gold, one label in text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-secondary.”

Keep each session scoped to **one component or one concern** to avoid timeouts.
